<p>YMYL content directly impacts people's financial decisions. Google applies stricter <a href="/blog/eeat-google-quality-guide/">E-E-A-T</a> evaluation to every accounting page it crawls. A tax advice article from a firm with no visible credentials, no author bios, and no reviews will not rank. Period.</p>
