<h3>Content Freshness</h3>
<p>Stale financial content is not just an SEO problem. It is a trust problem.</p>
<p>If a potential client sees outdated tax figures on your website, they will question your expertise. Update every piece of content at minimum once per year:</p>
<ul>
<li>Refresh tax thresholds and bracket amounts</li>
<li>Update filing deadlines</li>
<li>Add references to new tax laws</li>
<li>Replace outdated screenshots and examples</li>
<li>Update the dateModified <a href="/blog/schema-markup-seo-guide/">schema markup</a> on every page</li>
</ul>
