<p><strong>Expert roundups and guest posts</strong>. Write guest articles for local business publications. Offer expert commentary on tax law changes to journalists.</p>
<p><strong>Resource pages</strong>. Create definitive guides that other sites reference. A thorough guide to "[state] small business tax requirements" becomes a link magnet.</p>
